Package edu.mills.findeatfood

Implementation of the mobile application FINDEATFOOD.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DietaryFragment.OnDietOptionsSelectedListener
    Used for transferring ArrayList of ids for dietary and allergy options into MainActivity.
    ResultsFragment.ResultsListListener
    Used for transferring a recipe's recipe ID into MainActivity.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DietaryFragment
    Displays dietary restrictions in checkboxes.
    FavoritesFragment
    Retrieves a list of all of the recipes in the database.
    HomeFragment
    Displays home screen.
    HttpRequestUtilities
    Utility class for making HTTP requests to Yummly.
    IngredientsFragment
    Displays an editText and button.
    MainActivity
    The top-level activity for the app FindEatFood.
    RecipeDatabaseUtilities
    Provides an interface that connects to the database.
    RecipeDetailFragment
    Provides details about the recipe by giving its name, prep time, ingredients, etc.
    ResultsFragment
    Shows list of recipe results returned from the API.
    SQLiteRecipeOpenHelper
    Creates and updates the database for the app, FindEatFood.
    ValContainer<T>
    Generic container class that allows for safe getting and setting of an object.

Package edu.mills.findeatfood Description

Implementation of the mobile application FINDEATFOOD. Created for Mills CS 115: Mobile Application Development, Spring 2017.
